{"tid":474211,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"話老細錯，但原來係自己搞錯，應該如何自處？","createTime":"2017-11-20T03:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T04:29:11.000Z","uid":113545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3e2bcc726969f1fdca6b0c79e76b24c0cf5eefd6","tid":474211,"uid":113545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:10:01.000Z","msg":"可能今日星期一未清醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然好少事(掛...)<br />\n<br />\n老細whatsapp我<br />\n<br />\n老細：(語音)加碗粥呀<br />\n我：老細你send錯咗？<br />\n隔咗陣<br />\n老細：(語音)幫我叫阿姐去買大家樂早餐<br />\n我：OK<br />\n<br />\n然後我去叫阿姐買。<br />\n隔咗陣老細走過嚟問我send錯咩俾我？<br />\n我：加碗粥呀<br />\n老細：哦，係咩？send錯呀？<br />\n然後佢就走開咗。<br />\n<br />\n我再聽多次兩個語音，突然釘一聲，頂<br />\n應該係個wifi問題，接收出事<br />\n收到加粥先，再收到買早餐<br />\n其實應該係兩句次序掉轉咗收到<br />\n<br />\n我拿拿臨打電話叫阿姐買多碗粥，而加當乜事都冇發生。<br />\n但以老細角度嚟講，我咪話錯咗佢？？！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e874c3bf991632616b228f6e1f6877e80c9f7b18","tid":474211,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:11:30.000Z","msg":"SHOW 俾俾佢睇"},{"pid":"39e57f5e7eafe831eae3ab0fe6d73816c4039988","tid":474211,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35ae10d5e032f285aee754592ffeec1edb7942f","tid":474211,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:15:32.000Z","msg":"你又唔係屌佢，有乜錯唔錯"},{"pid":"66d2998ee3656b606361af6c5b55b70cdb26d2a7","tid":474211,"uid":113545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:21:34.000Z","msg":"佢會唔會以為我暗示佢  唔好搵我幫佢叫人買早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定我諗多咗<br />\n因為佢成日都搵我做啲濕星嘢"},{"pid":"00f6b4da1b0b82b781ce49a48452146cda834c54","tid":474211,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c